metadata.name: schnapoon_crowdfundingNFT
metadata.description:
Crowdfunding NFT for schnapoon to go to Las Vegas and attend SplinterFest!

If I win the competition at SplinterFest, I will give away a special NFT to anyone who has this NFT. If you don't win, I will give it to you if you win a future tournament. Also, my dream is to create the number one gaming guild in Asia, so you will be able to get preferential treatment there.
